      "asbval:evidence_quote": null,
      "asbval:note": "The paper describes MassQL as a query language and software ecosystem for mass spectrometry data analysis. No mention of unit testing, CI workflows, test-unit.yml, or repository testing infrastructure appears in any passage. The paper focuses on the language design, applications, and ecosystem adoption, not on software testing procedures.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-1038-s41592-025-02660-z",
