      "asbval:target_claim_text": "Tokenize domain-specific query strings (e.g., MassQL) into a stream of meaningful lexical units (keywords, operators, numeric literals, identifiers) to enable downstream parsing and AST construction. This is the first stage of a compiler/interpreter pipeline for mass-spectrometry",
