      "asbval:evidence_quote": "The parser transforms a query into an internal data structure that can be used by any programming language. The parsing is done by using the lark Python library (https://github.com/lark-parser/lark) and specific Python code to transform a MassQL query to a parse tree and into the internal data structure that organizes all query conditions and qualifiers.",
